    "This criterion was based on the rationale that if one inputter could derive the correct solution, the SAA was technically capable of providing an accurate triage assessment 43.",
    "Analyses for each inputter separately can be found in the Appendix.",
    "Data from LLMs were collected by one person only between November 28 th and 29 th 2023, as we used a predefined, one-shot prompt for all LLMs to circumvent input variation.",
    "We collected data for both the vignettes from our comparator dataset and those developed in this study.",
    "The prompt we used was adapted from two previous studies 12, 44 and stated \"Please give a triage classification for the following vignette."
  ],
